title: Deering Senior Recognized for Accomplishments (Portland Public School District)
text: ( Source : Portland Public School District ) Deering High School senior Salim Salim will be giving a TED ( Technology , Entertainment and Design ) talk this November in which he will be discussing topics around the significance of taking risks.
